title: BelowDeckMed: Plant-Based Riot
description:
Ring the alarms: there's a vegan on board Below Deck Mediterranean! Naturally this sends Kiko and the kitchen into disarray, and it doesn't help that these guests are AWFUL too. Meanwhile, Pete threatens to be professional, and Jess gets a sweet new hand accessory.

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
